headline: Costco (COST) Valuation in Focus After Shares Hit Fresh All-Time High
summary: Costco Wholesale (COST) just closed above $994 per share, a fresh high that may not shock loyal members but will definitely catch investor attention. There is no major news headline or event driving today’s move. However, any time a household name ticks higher, it is natural for investors to wonder if they are missing out on the next leg up or joining the rally too late. With Costco’s share price reaching such heights, questions around what the market is seeing—and what it might be...
